<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Password</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #d6d1cd, #969a97);
        }

        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
        }

        .navbar a {
            color: #5c67f2;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .navbar a:hover {
            background-color: #5c67f2;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-color: #5c67f2;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .navbar img {
            height: 40px;
            width: auto;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 80px; /* Adjusted for navbar height */
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
        }

        form {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 360px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        input[type="password"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        input[type="submit"] {
            background-color: #5c67f2;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        input[type="submit"]:hover {
            background-color: #4a54e1;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <a href="/"><img src="https://symbl.ai/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/What-Is-Named-Entity-Recognition-NER-and-What-Can-You-Do-with-It.png" alt="Home"></a>
        <div>
            <a href="/login">Log In</a>
            <a href="/signup">Sign Up</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Reset Your Password Below!</h2>
    <form action="/reset-password" method="post">
        <input type="hidden" name="name" value="{{name}}">
        <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Enter new password" required>
        <input type="submit" value="Reset Password">
    </form>
</body>

</html>
